25:32.064 --> 25:34.031
We have a lost child,
looking for its parents.

25:34.033 --> 25:36.000
If you are missing a child,

25:36.002 --> 25:38.402
please call lost and found.

25:49.248 --> 25:50.414
Kate, you're not eating.

25:50.416 --> 25:52.349
You okay?

25:52.351 --> 25:54.118
What's up with her?

25:59.725 --> 26:02.860
Are you kidding me?!
Oh! Why?

26:02.862 --> 26:04.562
Because we didn't make her
wear a t-shirt, that's why.

26:04.564 --> 26:06.830
No, no, Jack, you're only
gonna make it worse.

26:06.832 --> 26:08.098
Sit...

26:08.100 --> 26:09.533
Sit down. Seriously.

26:09.535 --> 26:10.768
I almost drowned!

26:10.770 --> 26:12.202
What?
Did you even care?

26:12.204 --> 26:13.571
When?
I tried to get
to the deep end,

26:13.573 --> 26:15.406
but you never watch me.
Hey. Calm down.

26:15.408 --> 26:16.674
You always watch them.
Kev, kev, kev.

26:16.676 --> 26:17.908
Come on...
Don't touch me.

26:17.910 --> 26:19.276
Watch yourself, pal.

26:19.278 --> 26:20.878
And you're so busy making sure

26:20.880 --> 26:22.112
that Kate's not
eating too much...

26:22.114 --> 26:23.447
Kev, calm down.

26:23.449 --> 26:25.282
...and... and Randall's
not too adopted,

26:25.284 --> 26:27.084
and meanwhile,
where's Kevin?

26:27.086 --> 26:28.285
Oh, guess what?

26:28.287 --> 26:30.354
He's dead.

26:30.356 --> 26:32.222
- Bud, we love you. We were watching...
- Don't touch me.

26:32.224 --> 26:33.257
I got this one.

26:33.259 --> 26:34.458
Hey, hey, hey,

26:34.460 --> 26:36.360
hey, come here.
Come here.

26:36.362 --> 26:37.394
What?
I'm sorry,
I'm sorry.

26:37.396 --> 26:38.696
I'm sorry.

26:38.698 --> 26:39.797
Okay? I should
have been watching.

26:39.799 --> 26:41.365
Okay?
You should have.

26:41.367 --> 26:43.067
And I said I was and I should
have been watching you, pal.

26:43.069 --> 26:44.234
I'm trying, okay?

26:44.236 --> 26:45.302
Look, I know that
I'm bigger than you.

26:45.304 --> 26:46.737
I know that
I'm an adult,

26:46.739 --> 26:49.707
but I... th-th-this is
my first time, okay?

26:49.709 --> 26:51.942
This is my first
time, too.

26:51.944 --> 26:54.211
